            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "ARTICLE 2 - CONFIDENTIALITY & ACCESS TO PERSONNEL FILES"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "heading",
            "attrs": {
                "nodeIndent": null,
                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                "style": "",
                "level": 4
            },
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2.1 "
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "bulletList",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "listItem",
                    "attrs": {
                        "closed": false,
                        "nested": false
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "attrs": {
                                "nodeIndent": 0,
                                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                                "style": ""
                            },
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "(a) An employee shall have the right to examine the contents of the employee's personnel file(s) during normal business hours, with the exception of confidential letters of reference. The employee may request and the Employer shall provide the names of authors of such confidential notes."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "listItem",
                    "attrs": {
                        "closed": false,
                        "nested": false
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "attrs": {
                                "nodeIndent": 0,
                                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                                "style": ""
                            },
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "(b) Except for confidential letters of reference and student teaching evaluations, no material on the employee's file related to the employee's performance shall be used in a hiring decision unless the employee has been notified that it has been placed on the file."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "heading",
            "attrs": {
                "nodeIndent": null,
                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                "style": "",
                "level": 4
            },
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2.2  Disciplinary Documents"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "bulletList",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "listItem",
                    "attrs": {
                        "closed": false,
                        "nested": false
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "attrs": {
                                "nodeIndent": 0,
                                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                                "style": ""
                            },
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "(a)  Subject to Article 12.5, where a letter imposing discipline, or other disciplinary documents, or both is being added to an employee’s file, the employee must, where possible, be notified and asked to initial any documents relating to the disciplinary action"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "listItem",
                    "attrs": {
                        "closed": false,
                        "nested": false
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "attrs": {
                                "nodeIndent": 0,
                                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                                "style": ""
                            },
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "marks": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "textHighlight",
                                            "attrs": {
                                                "highlight": "green"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "(b)  In the event of alleged distortion or error, the employee may request the inclusion of material pertinent to the alleged distortion or error. In the event of an error being established, the file shall be corrected and any erroneous material removed."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "attrs": {
                                "nodeIndent": 0,
                                "nodeTextAlignment": "left",
                                "nodeLineHeight": 2,
                                "style": ""
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
